name: 2 x 1k feat. new job perks
description:
Started a new job at Arc’teryx/Salomon so you know I had to use that juicy discount on my first pair of trail shoes. Excited to get into some legit trail running in the area!

Didn’t have a lotta time but wanted to take ‘em for a quick spin. 1k off, 1k on x 2 was all.
